=========================
L10n FR Account Tax UNECE
=========================

This module will auto-configure the parameters *UNECE Tax Type* and *UNECE Tax Category* on taxes that come from the *l10n_fr* module.

Installation
============

This module will be installed automatically if the *l10n_fr* and *account_tax_unece* modules are installed.

=====
